Cascadia Code v2407.24 (Regular weight only, woff2)
Source: https://github.com/microsoft/cascadia-code/releases/download/v2407.24/CascadiaCode-2407.24.zip
        (ttf/static/CascadiaCode-Regular.ttf -- the plain, non-Nerd-Font, non-PowerLine static
        Regular weight)
File:   CascadiaCode-Regular.woff2 -- losslessly repackaged from the .ttf above into woff2 via
        fontTools (fontTools.ttLib.TTFont, flavor="woff2"), since Microsoft's release only
        publishes ttf/otf, no woff2 build. Same glyph outlines/hinting/metrics as the source
        .ttf, just woff2's compressed container format, matching every other font in this
        directory being served as woff2.
